is\nsize will be considered small observing programs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 14 Jul 2018 01:18:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 Jul 2018 15:09:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-08"}
